-- Defense Minister Rejects Eliminating Germany's Military Draft, Bild Says
-- Patrick Donahue
-- 2010-07-23T05:42:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/defense-minister-rejects-eliminating-germany-s-military-draft-bild-says.html

          
          
             German Defense Minister Karl-Theodor
zu Guttenberg rejected a proposal to eliminate military
conscription as part of the country’s efforts to overhaul the
army, Bild reported. Such a move would be a “fatal mistake,”
Guttenberg said during a troop visit, the newspaper said.  
          
          


  


        